contributionDescription:
The Ideology Behind XOXO
The digital realm is vast, filled with countless creators and developers. Among them, women have been at the forefront, pushing boundaries, and redefining the landscape of web3. However, their contributions often go unnoticed or overshadowed. XOXO aims to change that narrative.

contributionLinks.description: XOXO celebrates the women in the web3 space.
